Zlatan Ibrahimovic set his sights on winning the Champions League with Paris Saint-Germain next season as the French side continued their pre-season preparations in Hong Kong.

The Swedish superstar looked as though he was feeling the intense heat as PSG trained on Saturday ahead of their latest warm-up match with local side Kitchee.

Ibrahimovic returns to action after a summer free of tournament football and was quickly back into his stride on the practice field.

And the striker was still smiling later as he took to the catwalk at a fashion show for Swiss watchmaker Hublot.

