'One of them is the Champions League. We have won two French championships in a row and the Coupe de la Ligue.

'Everyone dreams of winning the Champions League, and me too.'

Ibrahimovic, who watched the World Cup from the sidelines after Sweden failed to qualify, captained PSG in their last friendly - a 2-1 win at Nice on Wednesday night.

They reached the last eight of the Champions League last season before being eliminated on away goals by Chelsea.

PSG kick off their defence of the French title at Reims on August 8.

